Go! Go! Go! Go! Go!

01:28:44.420 --> 01:28:45.780
Go!

01:28:50.300 --> 01:28:51.980
You're right.

01:28:51.980 --> 01:28:53.740
You're right, Hayley.

01:28:53.740 --> 01:28:56.340
Thank you. Thank you.

01:28:57.340 --> 01:28:59.060
This is me.

01:28:59.060 --> 01:29:01.180
This is who I am.

01:29:01.180 --> 01:29:02.340
Thank you.

01:29:02.340 --> 01:29:04.220
Thank you for
helping me see it.

01:29:53.340 --> 01:29:55.020
What took you so long?

01:29:55.020 --> 01:29:57.420
You dropped this.
I had to.

01:29:57.420 --> 01:29:57.772
Yeah?

01:29:57.798 --> 01:29:59.180
You would have been
down there forever.

01:29:59.180 --> 01:30:00.540
Were you jerkin' off?

01:30:00.540 --> 01:30:03.132
Which do you wanna fuck
first, me or the knife?

01:30:03.158 --> 01:30:03.780
Uh-uh.

01:30:03.780 --> 01:30:07.820
You know how to use that?
Honor student, remember?

01:30:07.820 --> 01:30:10.940
Nothing I can't do
when I put my mind to it.

01:30:15.540 --> 01:30:17.620
Toss the knife in the backyard!

01:30:17.620 --> 01:30:18.740
Why?

01:30:18.740 --> 01:30:20.860
Or you'll shoot again?
Go on, shoot me.

01:30:20.860 --> 01:30:22.380
You're not gonna shoot me!

01:30:22.380 --> 01:30:25.500
It's not me you have to worry
about. It's Janelle.

01:30:27.020 --> 01:30:28.460
I called her.

01:30:28.460 --> 01:30:32.460
Told her I was Lieutenant Hayley
from the L.A.P.D.

01:30:32.460 --> 01:30:34.140
How far does she live, Jeff?

01:30:36.500 --> 01:30:38.700
Look over there.

01:30:38.700 --> 01:30:41.180
Look over there!

01:30:45.780 --> 01:30:48.500
The deal's still open.

01:30:48.500 --> 01:30:51.940
You put the noose around your
neck, you end this whole game.

01:30:51.940 --> 01:30:54.300
I will still clean up
all the evidence.

01:30:54.300 --> 01:30:56.500
You're running out of time!

01:30:57.860 --> 01:30:59.820
Or we can wait for her.

01:31:01.420 --> 01:31:04.220
I'll pull off my clothes,

01:31:04.220 --> 01:31:07.460
and I will run into her arms.

01:31:07.460 --> 01:31:09.340
What? Unless I hang myself?

01:31:12.860 --> 01:31:14.780
I'll find you.
I'll track you down!

01:31:14.780 --> 01:31:16.460
Assuming you knew
anything about me.

01:31:16.460 --> 01:31:18.300
Calabasas girl
who's dad teaches at UCW

01:31:18.300 --> 01:31:19.660
shouldn't be
that hard to find.

01:31:19.660 --> 01:31:22.780
You believed all that? Huh?

01:31:26.300 --> 01:31:27.860
Who are you?

01:31:28.860 --> 01:31:30.620
It's hard to say for sure.

01:31:32.540 --> 01:31:35.060
Maybe not a Calabasas girl.

01:31:35.060 --> 01:31:37.340
Maybe not the daughter
of a med school professor.

01:31:37.340 --> 01:31:40.940
Maybe not even a friend of Donna Mauer.
Maybe not even named Hayley.

01:31:45.980 --> 01:31:48.340
Who the hell are you?

01:31:50.740 --> 01:31:54.060
I am every little girl
you ever watched...

01:31:55.100 --> 01:31:57.900
touched, hurt,

01:31:57.900 --> 01:32:00.780
screwed, killed.

01:32:17.660 --> 01:32:19.700
She's gonna find it, Jeff.
No.

01:32:19.700 --> 01:32:21.180
She's gonna find it all.

01:32:21.180 --> 01:32:24.380
Put on the noose
and jump and I'll stop it.

01:32:27.100 --> 01:32:29.460
She'll never find out.

01:32:29.460 --> 01:32:31.860
She'll just think
you were some sad man

01:32:31.860 --> 01:32:33.980
who she never
should have left.

01:32:36.300 --> 01:32:37.180
Jeff?

01:32:44.140 --> 01:32:46.340
Bad things--

01:32:46.340 --> 01:32:48.060
Fucking awful things

01:32:48.060 --> 01:32:50.260
will happen to you in prison.
This is the only way.

01:32:50.260 --> 01:32:51.660
You'll wish you'd
killed yourself

01:32:51.660 --> 01:32:53.020
when you had the chance;
it's the only way.

01:32:55.100 --> 01:32:56.860
It's the only way, Jeff.

01:33:04.620 --> 01:33:05.500
Jeff!

01:33:22.620 --> 01:33:24.340
I didn't kill her.

01:33:28.220 --> 01:33:30.060
I just watched.

01:33:32.180 --> 01:33:34.780
I wanted to take pictures...

01:33:35.820 --> 01:33:38.380
but he wouldn't let me.

01:33:38.380 --> 01:33:41.100
It was me and another guy.

01:33:41.100 --> 01:33:43.140
I didn't do it. I swear.

01:33:43.140 --> 01:33:44.900
I'll tell you the name,

01:33:44.900 --> 01:33:47.180
and I'll help you find him.

01:33:47.180 --> 01:33:48.780
I'll help you find him.

01:33:52.660 --> 01:33:54.340
I know his name.

01:33:55.340 --> 01:33:58.140
I know his name, Jeff.

01:34:01.020 --> 01:34:03.100
You know what's funny?

01:34:07.620 --> 01:34:08.660
Jeff?

01:34:10.780 --> 01:34:13.860
Aaron told me you did it
before he killed himself.

01:34:19.180 --> 01:34:21.260
It was him. It wasn't me.

01:34:22.500 --> 01:34:23.380
Jeff.

01:34:26.020 --> 01:34:28.060
I don't care.

01:34:36.220 --> 01:34:38.220
Jeff?

01:35:25.980 --> 01:35:28.260
Don't worry.

01:35:28.260 --> 01:35:30.540
I promise I'll take
care of it all.

01:36:00.100 --> 01:36:01.820
Or not.

